n<br />\n仲有一種食法就係 係市場自己買處理好嘅魚鮮黎食<br />\n但當然最好係要你識揀 通常都係越貴就好食架啦"},{"pid":"ca7888e71d6cc4d642bf92f3da9a6c749c4b3683","tid":465342,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"我都睇緊<br />\n搵緊D米之連既舖<br />\n炸豬扒<br />\n拉麵<br />\n鰻魚等等<br />\n但大部份都係超級排隊店<br />\n要安排好最佳時間先得"},{"pid":"b58a2bf148c10ac2f18fb1a3bfe1cf5ebb008248","tid":465342,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"池袋無敵家"},{"pid":"01b2dca03409b065e925ab2c0ec94e488a9e314c","tid":465342,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你budget</blockquote><br />\n冇 set budget , 第一次諗住豪左佢<br />\n因為唔知有冇下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你所謂既豪係點豪法先？"}]}